title: 'Don't say we didn't warn you' - A phrase from China signals the trade war could get even worse

title: Corn futures surge, bringing May gain to 20% as soft commotities rally on Midwest flooding
text: Corn futures are surging, climbing to a near 3-year high, as heavy rain forecasts across major farming areas threaten to delay planting even further.

title: Many millennials say buying a home may finally be within reach

title: San Diego’s eSub raises $12 million for its construction management software

title: Airline Industry Warns Tariffs And Trade Disputes Are Threatening Travel Growth
text: Airlines have enjoyed a long period of stability since the dark days of 2008 and 2009, but sudden economic or geopolitical shocks could destabilize this low-margin, high-overhead industry at any time. The industry group IATA sees signs that trade disputes are starting to impact demand.

title: U.S. stock futures tumble as trade, global economy worries ramp up
text: U.S. stock futures fell sharply on Wednesday amid fresh concerns over U.S.-China trade negotiations and investors poured money into bonds.

title: 3-month yield tops 10-year rate in widest curve inversion since financial crisis

title: Stock Pickers' Ranks Soar As They Rush to Profit Off Trade War Volatility

title: DHL brings Africa eShop to 20 countries in a competitive nod to Jumia

title: Strategists see Wall Street moving higher despite trade war risks: Reuters poll

title: Huawei challenges legality of U.S. defense bill as sanctions fight ramps up

title: HSBC and UBS upgrade Malaysian stocks as trade war escalates
